title: The Green Queen
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Western, Fast food, Beer/Wine, Take-out, European
description: Operating summer months May to Sept only. Mälarpaviljongen restaurant opened this small organic food deli across the street. A few tables for eating-in. Has cold pressed juices, smoothies, snack foods, and usually 1 vegan suitable hot dish and 2 cold ones. No cash, card only.
